    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《奇异种子》是一款受《孢子》生物阶段启发的进化游戏，但它更注重“部件的意义”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你从一团不起眼的黏液球开始——那是从某棵奇怪的树上掉落的“奇异种子”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然这个世界上有无数的黏液球，但你与它们截然不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224660/extras/659e6c3bd445db3b3a724afaa83b61e7.poster.avif?t=1768927406\" width=1170 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224660/extras/659e6c3bd445db3b3a724afaa83b61e7.webm?t=1768927406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">进化</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败其他生物以收集它们的 DNA，解锁新的身体部件。不断重塑自己，尝试各种组合，打造终极形态。但请记住——平衡至关重要：强壮的躯干和强力的头部或许能赢得战斗，可如果你追不上猎物，它们又有何用？7 个部位槽位、超过 40 种生物可供发掘，你将拥有超过一千万种进化组合的可能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224660/extras/0a23c249955983e53a8f77887287de05.poster.avif?t=1768927406\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224660/extras/0a23c249955983e53a8f77887287de05.webm?t=1768927406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">探索</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索 10 多种独特生态区，从郁郁葱葱的森林、金色沙滩，到现代都市，甚至炽热的火山之心。每个环境都有其独特的挑战。身体太大而挤不过狭窄的通道？那就进化成更小的形态。腿太短跳不上高台？那就长出翅膀，展翅飞翔！这个世界充满了秘密——你能一一发现它们吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224660/extras/2696095b81246915a0112dcf9ac9f3d7.poster.avif?t=1768927406\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224660/extras/2696095b81246915a0112dcf9ac9f3d7.webm?t=1768927406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别被这多彩的世界所迷惑——《奇异种子》的世界危机四伏。从普通的蜥蜴到凶猛的类魂系 Boss，危险无处不在。胜利不仅取决于反应，更取决于你的“部位搭配”。正确的组合，往往就是生与死的差别。如果你足够聪明，或许还能找到一些“巧妙取胜”的办法！</p>",
